<paragraph id="9DDF1DDDA4BEB04E0449AB79255B01D9" pageId="0" pageNumber="143">Central and southern Italy, south-western Sardinia, Sicily, northern Algeria and Tunisia and north-eastern Spain.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
